snippet.title: Day Life, away from battles｜Mad World - Age of Darkness - MMORPG
snippet.description:
Mad World Official Launch on April 27th (Thur)
✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com

[Gathering/Mining] Don’t miss out the various materials you can gather and mine in Mad World! They may serve as materials for fancy equipment.
[Cooking] Learn recipe for each dish and say goodbye to starvation!
[Crafting] Materials from monsters will serve as powerful equipment for you.
[Black Market] You may trade items with other survivors.
=====================================
We have reached 300 thousand pre-registrators!
Now let’s go for 500 thousand!

Pre-register now if you have not taken part in our pre-registration events yet!

✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com
=====================================
✨MadWorld official site
👉Discord: https://discord.gg/madworldmmo
👉Homepage: https://www.madworldmmo.com
